727679f-a.title: Queens: Parsons Boulevard - 82nd Road
727679f-a.text:
Parsons Boulevard (left), north from 82nd Road toward
Union Turnpike, in the valley. The area in the immediate
foreground is part of the grounds where the Queens General
Hospital is going up.
P. L. Sperr  March 25, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS
